.jumbotron
  .container
    h1.jumbotron-content #{ site.name } Provides #{ site.tagline }

.container#intro
  .row
    .col-sm-8
      .intro-box.wow.fadeInDown
        h2 Anticorrosive Protection System
        p.lead The PCS anticorrosive protection system provides splash zone protection for steel structures, concrete, and wood.
      .intro-box.wow.fadeInRightBig
        h2 Ideal for Severe Conditions
        p.lead The PCS system is ideal for environments where conditions are too severe for paint systems, epoxies and other conventional forms of protection.
      .intro-box.wow.fadeInLeftBig
        h2 Stops Corrosion
        p.lead The PCS system seals the oxygen and water and effectively stops corrosion on metal surfaces.
    .col-sm-4.text-center
      img(src='img/pipe.png', alt='', height='500')

section.section-dark.section-theme-km.section-padded
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-4
        p: img.img-responsive.wow.pulse(src='img/intro-1.png', alt='', data-wow-delay='1s')
      .col-sm-8
        h2 Other Features
        p.lead.wow.fadeInUp The system also prevents loosening and corrosion of steel reinforcement in concrete piles. The PCS system encapsulates pier piles, riser tubes and pipes exposed in intertidal zones and splash.
        p.lead.wow.fadeInDown The system accommodates cylindrical piles and H configurations and support members, reinforcement, supports and other uneven surfaces.

