    hr
    .row.wow.fadeInLeftBig
      .col-sm-6.pad-top
        h3 PCS Mastic
        p.lead Petrolatum Mastic is used to fill cavities based on uneven surfaces before wrapping PCS Anti corrosion tape.
      .col-sm-6
        img.img-responsive(src='img/mastic.png', alt='')
    hr
    .row.wow.fadeInRightBig
      .col-sm-6.pad-top
        h3 PCS Liner 6000
        p.lead The PC&reg; 6000HD series consists of a proprietary polymer polyolefin, fully protected against UV degradation and oxidation with technically advanced stabilization package
      .col-sm-6
        img.img-responsive(src='img/liner.png', alt='')
    hr
    .row.wow.fadeInLeftBig
      .col-sm-6.pad-top
        h3 Petro Tape
        p.lead Synthetic adhesive fabric impregnated and coated with a material based on waxes and oils, covered with vaseline-based compounds and inert fibers.
      .col-sm-6
